bootconf (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * YAML-driven boot-time configuration for readonly Linux
  * Hostname and timezone configuration
  * SSH host key generation and service management
  * WiFi (wpa_supplicant) configuration
  * User account provisioning via systemd-sysusers
  * File provisioning with write-protect mechanism
  * Comprehensive input validation

